This makes her the first female Korean solo artiste to attain such heights on the streaming platform, reported Allkpop yesterday.

Her fellow BlackPink member Lisa Manoban is the other female K-Pop soloist in Spotify to have crossed the 20-million monthly listener mark.
Their dominance on YouTube is also evident as Jennie and Lisa near a billion views with their respective current hits Solo and Money.
